blockingFindings[9]{id,dimension,phaseRef,description}:
  B-01,feature-coverage,Phase 0,ConvergeConfig schema table missing harness field row (lines 43-54). Phase 0 contracts-agent will produce incomplete convergence-tier.schema.md.
  B-02,feature-coverage,Phase 12,/loom-converge flag table missing --resume and --resume-config entries (lines 199-205). Library catalog tests and wiring will be incomplete.
  B-03,strategy,Phase 14,Token-cost ceiling AC (--autoconverge total cost <= 1.5x manual baseline) not automatable — spawn count and token cost are distinct metrics; no phase instruments cost tracking.
  B-04,ux,driver-stdout,Progress visibility during multi-iteration autoconverge run is undefined. No specification for iteration counter, current blockingCount, or per-iteration output line.
  B-05,ux,Phase 10,Circuit breaker halt messages have no defined presentation format. Five breakers (SCOPE_EXPANSION/STALL/REGRESSION/BUDGET_EXHAUSTED/MAX_ITERATIONS) all halt without specified user-facing text or recovery commands.
  B-06,ux,Phase 5+10,--auto vs SCOPE_EXPANSION conflict — plan promises non-interactive end-to-end under --auto BUT also says SCOPE_EXPANSION prompts user. Mutually exclusive; must resolve.
  B-07,phasing,Phase 13,Phase 13 convergence target (line 860) references --autoconverge but Phase 13 lists only Phase 5+11 as deps. Should belong to Phase 14 only; copy-paste artifact from Phase 10.
  B-08,phasing,Phase 5+11,Phase 5 ACs require driver to write snapshot files for verification but the snapshot helper lives in Phase 11 (W4). Phase 5's M-01 gate is untestable until Phase 11 ships.
  B-09,parallelization,Phase 10+12,library.yaml double-write conflict — Phase 10 AC line 857 writes library.yaml; Phase 12 also declares sole ownership of library.yaml in W5. Will clobber or duplicate entries.

warningFindings[31]{id,dimension,phaseRef,description}:
  W-01,feature-coverage,Phase 0,ConvergeConfig timestamp precision not locked (ISO 8601 ms vs s) — affects stall-detection regression checks
  W-02,feature-coverage,Phase 0,IterationSnapshot slug derivation underspecified for files with multiple dots (PLAN-x.v2.md ambiguous)
  W-03,feature-coverage,Phase 0,ConvergenceFindings missing reviewerAgent attribution field — once aggregated, origin of each finding is lost
  W-04,feature-coverage,Phase 10,/loom-plan create lacks --dry-run for previewing generated converge.config before driver invocation
  W-05,feature-coverage,Phase 10,/loom-converge missing --output-dir for concurrent runs or CI environments
  W-06,strategy,Phase 5,Phase 5 ACs reference snapshot assertions that depend on Phase 11 (W4) helper — deferred-test caveat not annotated
  W-07,strategy,Phase 6+7,Phase 6 and Phase 7 wave-parallel-eligible but Phase 7 depends on Phase 6 explicitly — verify wave executor respects ordering
  W-08,strategy,Phase 14,'structurally equivalent final plans (within whitespace)' assertion in F-03 won't survive non-deterministic LLM outputs; replace with shape check
  W-09,strategy,Phase 1,Missing-subject field path on old-style converge.config has no user-facing message (only schema validation)
  W-10,ux,Phase 1+10,critique.toon vs findings.toon relationship not explained to user; two artifacts with different field names but no distinguishing UX
  W-11,ux,Phase 7,--skip-critic semantic scope underspecified (stale critique.toon handling not addressed; flag combination with --autoconverge not in table)
  W-12,ux,Phase 5,Snapshot rollback UX described only as risk-table footnote (C-07); no command/workflow for listing/diffing/restoring snapshots
  W-13,ux,driver-output,Empty state (blockingCount=0 at iter 1) success message format undefined
  W-14,ux,changelog,Convergence trajectory summary format and terminal-echo behavior undefined
  W-15,ux,Phase 9,Harness partial failure (1 of 6 reviewers fails) user-facing warning missing
  W-16,ux,Phase 10,critique.toon location never advertised — Step 1.7 completion does not echo path or predictedBlockingCount addressed
  W-17,phasing,Phase 8,Phase 8 dep annotation contradictory — 'parallel; Phase 6 dep' is self-inconsistent
  W-18,phasing,Phase 9+0,Phase 9 aggregator has no AgentResult.severity → ConvergenceFindings.severity mapping table; silent undercount risk
  W-19,phasing,Wave 3,W3 advertised as parallel but Phases 6→7→8 form serial chain via dependency declarations
  W-20,phasing,Phase 9,Phase 9 dependency on Phase 2 is reversed causality (Phase 9 produces what Phase 2 documents consuming)
  W-21,phasing,Phase 10,Phase 10 convergence target references live planning file (ROADMAP-kit-native-skills.md) instead of test fixture
  W-22,phasing,Milestones,M-02 phases list omits Phase 13 even though Phase 14 depends on Phase 13
  W-23,parallelization,Phase 7+10,Phase 10's create.md edit depends on Phase 7's committed state; no inter-wave handoff protocol or grep gate defined
  W-24,parallelization,Phase 9,Phase 9 declared W4 with Phase 10 dependency — they cannot run in parallel within W4 (serial pair masquerading as parallel wave)
  W-25,parallelization,Wave 1,W1 phases 1-4 share convergence-driver.md; correctly serial via deps but wave label implies parallelism
  W-26,parallelization,Phase 12,Phase 12 wiring scope omits Phase 9 dep — execution-conventions.md update needs to cover TS harness pattern
  W-27,agentic-workflow,Phase 5,Phase 5 bundles two structurally distinct features (scope-guard + auto-snapshot); split candidates
  W-28,agentic-workflow,Phase 9,Phase 9 TS implementation spec underconstrained — agent spawn mechanism from TS not specified; loom-converge.md not in files-in; AgentResult type undefined
  W-29,agentic-workflow,Phase 10,Phase 10 --autoconverge invocation hedges ('or the equivalent existing entry'); no starting-state note for post-Phase-7 create.md
  W-30,agentic-workflow,Phase 13,Phase 13 canned-harness invocation pattern underspecified (module vs spawn); fixture path resolution ambiguous; resume scenario setup undefined
  W-31,agentic-workflow,Phase 14,Phase 14 file-in count at warning boundary (17); pre/post-critic blocking-count engineering undefined for canned reviewers

