summary:
  totalFindings: 60
  blocking: 9
  warning: 31
  info: 20
  crossCuttingBlocking: 2 (CC-01, CC-02)
  passEvaluation: "Pass-1 review of a 15-phase 1202-line plan: 60 findings within expected range. 9 blocking is high but consistent with kit-native-skills pass-1 (8 blocking) on a similar-sized plan. Convergence trajectory expected to mirror prior pattern (~3 review-integrate passes) — exactly the problem this plan exists to solve."
  recommendedPath: "Run /loom-plan create --review-integrate to apply these 60 findings, then re-review. Two passes likely sufficient. CC-01 (Phase 5+11) and CC-02 (library.yaml) are the load-bearing fixes; everything else is mechanical."
  ironyNote: "Meta-recursion: this plan creates --autoconverge to avoid the very ~3-pass cycle this review just confirmed is the current state. Each manual --review-integrate pass on this plan validates the need for the plan itself."
